{
  "stem": "27.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The last one, the new one, he built it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't mean he.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean his company built it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Otherwise, he was in there heavy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was very, very big turn with the Czech government, mostly because they were all governmental jobs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was very successful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody did-- [CRYING] Nobody can ask for a better father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I hope I'd be half of-- as good-- [CRYING] --as he was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He lived for the children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] His dream was when the boys grow up, everyone have a different-- like he always wanted me to be a banker, because I was so good in math.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was outstanding always in math.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was my favorite subject.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He always said, you be the banker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He already figured it out-- provided us with everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My mother was an angel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[CRYING] They really did their best to help us, to improve us, to make better, easier life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because he was working very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was in that business, but although the business was opened only five and a half days-- Saturday noon and no Saturday/ Sunday.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But whenever he was Sunday at home, and said all he done is just breaking his head.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The books, you know, he did the books and everything then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He brought more ways in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he taught me already at the age of 10, how to do things and helped me a life-- helped me a lot in life-- what I learned from my father.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the Germans?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excellent-- very good life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I told you, they were well-to-do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had everything we needed, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish life was, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I belonged to the organization, Zionist-- Kadima.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
